            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2042%3A1-44%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EWarning%20to%20Stay%20in%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20all%20the%20military%20leaders%2C%20including%20Johanan%20son%20of%20Kareah%20and%20Jezaniah%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E42%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20version%20reads%20%3Cem%3EAzariah%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20compare%2043%3A2.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20son%20of%20Hoshaiah%2C%20and%20all%20the%20people%2C%20from%20the%20least%20to%20the%20greatest%2C%20approached%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EJeremiah%20the%20prophet.%20They%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20pray%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20for%20us.%20As%20you%20can%20see%2C%20we%20are%20only%20a%20tiny%20remnant%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20were%20before.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EPray%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20will%20show%20us%20what%20to%20do%20and%20where%20to%20go.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAll%20right%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Jeremiah%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20pray%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20as%20you%20have%20asked%2C%20and%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20everything%20he%20says.%20I%20will%20hide%20nothing%20from%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20they%20said%20to%20Jeremiah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMay%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20be%20a%20faithful%20witness%20against%20us%20if%20we%20refuse%20to%20obey%20whatever%20he%20tells%20us%20to%20do!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EWhether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20we%20will%20obey%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20to%20whom%20we%20are%20sending%20you%20with%20our%20plea.%20For%20if%20we%20obey%20him%2C%20everything%20will%20turn%20out%20well%20for%20us.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ETen%20days%20later%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20his%20reply%20to%20Jeremiah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20he%20called%20for%20Johanan%20son%20of%20Kareah%20and%20the%20other%20military%20leaders%2C%20and%20for%20all%20the%20people%2C%20from%20the%20least%20to%20the%20greatest.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20sent%20me%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20with%20your%20request%2C%20and%20this%20is%20his%20reply%3A%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BStay%20here%20in%20this%20land.%20If%20you%20do%2C%20I%20will%20build%20you%20up%20and%20not%20tear%20you%20down%3B%20I%20will%20plant%20you%20and%20not%20uproot%20you.%20For%20I%20am%20sorry%20about%20all%20the%20punishment%20I%20have%20had%20to%20bring%20upon%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EDo%20not%20fear%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20anymore%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%26%23x2018%3BFor%20I%20am%20with%20you%20and%20will%20save%20you%20and%20rescue%20you%20from%20his%20power.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20be%20merciful%20to%20you%20by%20making%20him%20kind%2C%20so%20he%20will%20let%20you%20stay%20here%20in%20your%20land.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20if%20you%20refuse%20to%20obey%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20and%20if%20you%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWe%20will%20not%20stay%20here%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Einstead%2C%20we%20will%20go%20to%20Egypt%20where%20we%20will%20be%20free%20from%20war%2C%20the%20call%20to%20arms%2C%20and%20hunger%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3Ethen%20hear%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20message%20to%20the%20remnant%20of%20Judah.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BIf%20you%20are%20determined%20to%20go%20to%20Egypt%20and%20live%20there%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20very%20war%20and%20famine%20you%20fear%20will%20catch%20up%20to%20you%2C%20and%20you%20will%20die%20there.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20is%20the%20fate%20awaiting%20every%20one%20of%20you%20who%20insists%20on%20going%20to%20live%20in%20Egypt.%20Yes%2C%20you%20will%20die%20from%20war%2C%20famine%2C%20and%20disease.%20None%20of%20you%20will%20escape%20the%20disaster%20I%20will%20bring%20upon%20you%20there.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_18%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BJust%20as%20my%20anger%20and%20fury%20have%20been%20poured%20out%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20so%20they%20will%20be%20poured%20out%20on%20you%20when%20you%20enter%20Egypt.%20You%20will%20be%20an%20object%20of%20damnation%2C%20horror%2C%20cursing%2C%20and%20mockery.%20And%20you%20will%20never%20see%20your%20homeland%20again.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_19%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BListen%2C%20you%20remnant%20of%20Judah.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20told%20you%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BDo%20not%20go%20to%20Egypt!%26%23x2019%3B%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20forget%20this%20warning%20I%20have%20given%20you%20today.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_20%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20you%20were%20not%20being%20honest%20when%20you%20sent%20me%20to%20pray%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20for%20you.%20You%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BJust%20tell%20us%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20says%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20it!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_21%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20today%20I%20have%20told%20you%20exactly%20what%20he%20said%2C%20but%20you%20will%20not%20obey%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20any%20better%20now%20than%20you%20have%20in%20the%20past.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_42_22%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2242%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20you%20will%20die%20from%20war%2C%20famine%2C%20and%20disease%20in%20Egypt%2C%20where%20you%20insist%20on%20going.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_43_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2243%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%